close_reason: Scaffolder is TypeScript-first
body: "## Revised pre-release (2026-06-24) by [[pm-2p7a]] / [[pm-m1uz]]\n\nAs originally landed (commit 73c0e729) this scaffolder emitted a `build` script and a compiled `./index.js` manifest entry. That intermediate state was superseded **before any release** by the TypeScript-only loading model ([[pm-m1uz]]): the scaffolder now emits `typecheck`/`test` scripts (no `build`), a `noEmit` tsconfig, and points the manifest `entry` at `./index.ts` itself (loaded directly via Node native type stripping). Title corrected to the net-shipped state so the Unreleased changelog is accurate."
